# Server Data Conventions (Fetching & Mutations)

---

## 1. File Placement

```
app/
└── {route}/
    ├── page.tsx        # Server Component — reads
    ├── actions.ts      # Server Actions — writes
    ├── loading.tsx     # Suspense fallback
    └── error.tsx       # Error boundary
```

---

## 2. Data Fetching (Server Components)

Fetch trực tiếp trong Server Component. Lấy token từ `cookies()`.

```tsx
// app/room/page.tsx
import { cookies } from "next/headers"
import { getRooms } from "@/lib/endpoints/room"

export default async function RoomPage() {
  const token = cookies().get("auth-token")?.value
  const { data } = await getRooms({}, token)

  return (
    <main>
      {data.content.map((room) => (
        <RoomCard key={room.id} room={room} />
      ))}
    </main>
  )
}
```

### Caching

| Option                                   | Khi nào dùng                                 |
| ---------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| `{ next: { revalidate: 60 } }`           | Data ít thay đổi, chấp nhận stale tối đa 60s |
| `{ cache: "no-store" }`                  | Data phải luôn fresh                         |
| `export const dynamic = "force-dynamic"` | Toàn bộ page luôn dynamic                    |

Truyền cache option qua `api()`:

```ts
getRooms({}, token) // default — Next.js tự quyết định
api<RoomResponse>("/api/v1/rooms", { next: { revalidate: 60 } })
api<RoomResponse>("/api/v1/rooms", { cache: "no-store" })
```

---

## 3. Server Actions (Mutations)

Đặt trong `app/{route}/actions.ts`. Luôn gọi `revalidatePath()` sau mutation.

```ts
// app/room/actions.ts
"use server"

import { cookies } from "next/headers"
import { revalidatePath } from "next/cache"
import { createRoom, updateRoom, deleteRoom } from "@/lib/endpoints/room"
import type { RoomRequest } from "@/types/room"

function getToken() {
  return cookies().get("auth-token")?.value
}

export async function createRoomAction(data: RoomRequest) {
  const result = await createRoom(data, getToken())
  revalidatePath("/room")
  return result
}

export async function updateRoomAction(id: number, data: RoomRequest) {
  const result = await updateRoom(id, data, getToken())
  revalidatePath("/room")
  revalidatePath(`/room/${id}`)
  return result
}

export async function deleteRoomAction(id: number) {
  const result = await deleteRoom(id, getToken())
  revalidatePath("/room")
  return result
}
```

---

## 4. Error Boundary

```tsx
// app/room/error.tsx
"use client"

export default function RoomError({
  error,
  reset,
}: {
  error: Error
  reset: () => void
}) {
  return (
    <div className="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 p-8">
      <p className="text-destructive">{error.message}</p>
      <button onClick={reset}>Thử lại</button>
    </div>
  )
}
```

> Server Components để lỗi bubble tự nhiên lên `error.tsx` — không cần try/catch trong page.

---

## 5. Loading UI

```tsx
// app/room/loading.tsx
export default function RoomLoading() {
  return <div>Đang tải...</div>
}
```

---

## Rules

- **Server Components** cho reads — không dùng `"use client"` chỉ để fetch.
- **Server Actions** cho writes — đặt trong `actions.ts` cùng route.
- Token luôn lấy từ `cookies()` trong Server context.
- `revalidatePath()` bắt buộc sau mỗi mutation.
- `error.tsx` đặt cạnh `page.tsx` để catch lỗi Server Component.
- Không try/catch trong Server Component pages — để lỗi bubble lên `error.tsx`.
